Third Department,

February, 1971

(February 3, 1971) In the Matter of the Designation of J. Clarence Herlihy, Presiding Justice, Supreme Court, Appellate Division, Third Judicial Department, as a Member of the Court on the Judiciary.

Herlihy, P. J., Reynolds, Staley, Jr., Greenblott, Cooke and Sweeney, JJ., concur.
